<p id="_d5ab0123-0c48-45da-b91b-21e714dcc272">as a weighted mean. The fractional uncertainty was evaluated to be approximately <stem type="MathML"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mn>4.3</mn><mo>&#215;</mo><msup><mrow><mn>10</mn></mrow><mrow><mrow><mi>&#8722;</mi><mn>10</mn></mrow></mrow></msup></math></stem> for a 0.01 s averaging time <eref type="inline" bibitemid="bitou" citeas="[3]">[3]</eref>. For the recommendation this uncertainty was rounded to <stem type="MathML"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mn>5</mn><mo>&#215;</mo><msup><mrow><mn>10</mn></mrow><mrow><mrow><mi>&#8722;</mi><mn>10</mn></mrow></mrow></msup></math></stem>.</p></clause>
